div.div:
Sharing:
Alice wants to share data with her Doctor Bob.
Alice generates a share_key and encrypts it with share_code.
Alice encryptes the days to share with share_key. Alice also truncates/creates the period stats.
Alice publishes the days and the stats under a share_id.
Alice creates a URL with the share_id: https://share.cyla.app/#share_id
Alice sends that link to Bob.
Bob can now visit the link retreive and decrypt the shared days by entering the share_code.
